      <title>交易员加大对大幅降息的押注，法国债券风险指数下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/french-bond-risk-gauge-eases-as-traders-boost-bets-on-jumbo-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于货币市场预期欧洲央行将加快降息，法国债券市场在动荡的一周内出现上涨，消除了与德国债券相比表现不佳的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/french-bond-risk-gauge-eases-as-traders-boost-bets-on-jumbo-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 17:26:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡珀称放松管制可能会释放“动物精神”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-29/deregulation-could-unleash-animal-spirits-hooper-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Invesco 首席全球市场策略师克里斯蒂娜·胡珀 (Kristina Hooper) 表示，即将上任的特朗普政府放松监管的想法激发了市场的一些动物精神。她在“彭博监视”节目中谈到了 2025 年投资者面临的风险。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-29/deregulation-could-unleash-animal-spirits-hooper-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 16:45:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通预计欧洲央行 12 月将降息半个百分点 因经济疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/jpmorgan-sees-half-point-ecb-cut-in-december-as-economy-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司因欧盟经济活动放缓，提前呼吁欧洲央行将利率下调半个百分点至12月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/jpmorgan-sees-half-point-ecb-cut-in-december-as-economy-weakens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 16:34:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西股市因支出计划而周跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西市场有望迎来数月来最糟糕的一周，因为备受吹捧的削减政府支出计划效果远不及预期，加剧了人们对该国预算的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/brazil-markets-set-for-worst-week-in-two-years-on-spending-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 13:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特基金重点转移影响部分项目预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/saudi-arabia-s-pif-is-shifting-priorities-may-cut-some-project-budgets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯的主权财富基金正准备连续第二年削减一些地方项目的预算，同时增加总体支出，这反映出该国在万亿美元的经济改革计划中优先事项的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/saudi-arabia-s-pif-is-shifting-priorities-may-cut-some-project-budgets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 12:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利联合信贷银行将在与法国农业信贷银行的谈判中讨论 Amundi 事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/unicredit-plans-to-meet-credit-agricole-to-discuss-banco-bpm-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来几周，意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 和法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 的高管将齐聚一堂，讨论意大利联合信贷银行收购国内竞争对手一事，届时两家公司之间还将讨论一项至关重要的分销协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/unicredit-plans-to-meet-credit-agricole-to-discuss-banco-bpm-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 09:40:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股涨势盖过关税忧虑，欧洲股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/european-stocks-pause-as-tariff-risks-french-politics-weigh</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周五上涨，盘尾上涨，因科技股和资源相关股的涨幅抵消了对贸易关税和法国近期政治动荡的持续担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/european-stocks-pause-as-tariff-risks-french-politics-weigh</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 08:19:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走弱和乌克兰风险上升推动黄金上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/gold-steady-with-fed-rate-path-and-ukraine-risks-in-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走弱且乌克兰紧张局势加剧提振避险资产需求，黄金价格连续第四天上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/gold-steady-with-fed-rate-path-and-ukraine-risks-in-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 00:29:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>停火和 OPEC+ 不确定性导致油价在清淡交易中波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对 OPEC+ 的生产计划以及以色列和黎巴嫩真主党之间的停战协议的持久性的猜测，油价在假期后的清淡交易中波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-29</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 23:29:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：科技股在短线交易中推动美国股市走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市创下新高，美国国债收益率下跌，而有关当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将缓和其最极端的贸易政策的猜测导致美元创下三个月来最大单周跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-stocks-to-slip-as-treasury-trading-resumes-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 22:55:44 GMT</pubDate>
